N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2200.13 - Effect of these regulations on leases and other rental agreements

State Regulations

The provisions of any lease or other rental agreement
shall remain in force pursuant to the terms thereof, except insofar as those
provisions are inconsistent with the Rent Law or these
regulations. Notes
